%N A392842 Number of trailing zeros in a type of Zeckendorf expansion based on Fibonacci numbers of even index.
%C A392842 This sequence is the limit, as k goes to infinity, of the finite sequences (A035614(F(2k)-i), i=2..F(2k)), where F(k) = A000045(k) is the k-th Fibonacci number.
%C A392842 Here are the first few such finite sequences:
%C A392842   k=2: 1, 0
%C A392842   k=3: 1, 0, 3, 0, 2, 1, 0
%C A392842   k=4: 1, 0, 3, 0, 2, 1, 0, 5, 0, 2, 1, 0, 4, 1, 0, 3, 0, 2, 1, 0
%Y A392842 Cf. A035614, A392841, A001906, A000045.
%K A392842 nonn
%O A392842 1,3
